name: Solé
notes: The artist has several 6+ year old songs on their YouTube account, mainly featuring a woman rapping. Jump to around 5 months ago, and they started releasing songs mostly in a pop genre, but very notable jumps from genres in some songs like in "unbound", or even in different languages like in "Mon Style", or "Ma copine à moi". "Le Chat et la Souris" also has a male rapper rapping in French.
